i hate my life. i know alot of people say that but i really do! and i have for 2 years. since september of 2002. iim sure everyone knows that story, some may not belive it. but that's your problem not mine, and it's all true. i wish it wasnt but it is. :'( i wanna die soooo bad! but i cant do that to others around me. i wish i was never born. that would make everything so much easier. but im so thankful for those who care. who knows what i'd be doen if they wernt here. and you know who you are ...

I couldn't sleep last night

Best friends with the boogie man

Running on empty once again
